metadata.name: Shift your focus
metadata.description: Each of us has our own unique interpretation of the world, shaped by the things we choose to pay attention to. Our focus directs the flow of our energy, and at times, the distractions of life can cloud our vision, preventing us from seeing all of the beauty that surrounds us. It is essential to find balance in the chaos, and to understand that life's complexities are often most effectively comprehended through an abstract lens. By shifting our focus and changing our perspective, we can gain a deeper appreciation of the world and all of the beauty around us.
